public static DefaultSplunkConfigurationFactory mockComponent(final Service service, final Socket socket) {     return new DefaultSplunkConfigurationFactory() {          @Override         public SplunkConfiguration parseMap(Map<String, Object> parameters) {             return new MockConnectionSettings(service, socket).         }     }. }
